{"tid":1843344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廣東省：公共場所強制全民戴口罩","createTime":"2020-01-26T07:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:32:13.000Z","uid":7971,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a39fb4ddb745dd41b3bfb785553f375e81b0cf61","tid":1843344,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:13:50.000Z","msg":"【廣東省：公共場所強制全民戴口罩】<br />\n【違者會被追責或被嚴懲】<br />\n<br />\n廣東省發布最新規定，因應武漢肺炎疫情，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民眾出入公共場所必須要戴口罩，否則會被追究責任。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n公共場所包括酒店、餐廳、娛樂場所、體育館、商店、圖書館等地。<br />\n<br />\n所有公共場所經營者必須檢查所有人士，確保配戴口罩後才可以進入場所，在入口處設有清晰的提示，並勸阻未戴口罩者。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n#口罩"},{"pid":"5a2aabba7bd167199585aadd5cadc027076d5571","tid":1843344,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"德政"},{"pid":"056ccebcc3d45c17026d6ddf6bbd86f4185a5199","tid":1843344,"uid":7971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"港共: am I a joke to you"},{"pid":"b1bcc367f099ca0bee067be9716110d784d28c3c","tid":1843344,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"朦面緊急法呢個時候先係要用"},{"pid":"2f8fdca99587f2a8da105ae6e86983206ff4619a","tid":1843344,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"等深圳封關 應該仲快過港共封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b131149b0d74ddf1aa876ad8f2adf193ce92ba","tid":1843344,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"第一次希望香港係廣東省一分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf723e1c1d45a5816ab61821fd9f9ab7768d87e","tid":1843344,"uid":7971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82b131149b0d74ddf1aa876ad8f2adf193ce92ba","tid":1843344,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"第一次希望香